text:
Config is Reusable!
{
  $schema: "https://docs.renovatebot.com/renovate-schema.json",
  extends: [
    "github&gt;paddyroddy/.github//renovate/default-config.json5",
    "schedule:monthly",
  ],
  "pre-commit": {
    fileMatch: [
      "precommit/general/general-hooks.yml",
      "precommit/latex/latex-hooks.yml",
      "precommit/python/python-hooks.yml",
    ],
  },
}

See in action: https://github.com/paddyroddy/.github/blob/main/.renovaterc.json5
